data.description: Welcome home! This property features a large living room with high ceilings and a cozy fireplace. With two bedrooms, two baths, and a two-car garage, comfort and convenience abound. Don't forget to enjoy the screened patio, perfect for entertaining or relaxing with a glass of wine. Located near the Medical Center, Dining and Shopping, this home offers both luxury and convenience. Don't miss out - schedule a viewing today!
